{"tid":2488781,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李家超指各部隊將加入中式步操元素彰顯國家情懷","createTime":"2021-04-14T12:46:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T15:23:56.000Z","uid":240362,"like":17,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"c16292aee689f689eb9ab9df12934a4cb781607a","tid":2488781,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T12:46:32.000Z","msg":"保安局局長李家超表示，明日是本港首個「全民國家安全教育日」，特區政府紀律部隊5間訓練學校都舉辦開放日，活動包括步操等，各部隊將加入中式步操元素，以彰顯國家情懷，加強國家安全意識。<br />\n<br />\n李家超在網上撰文說，支持各部門按實際情況，包括訓練及其他工作安排需要，建立一套既有中式步操元素，又符合部門發展的步操。<br />\n<br />\n李家超說，明日各紀律部隊加入中式步操作為表演項目，是發展香港步操的重要一步，讓步操可按香港實際情況，邁向既有中式步操元素，又擁有香港特色的多元發展。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1585791-20210414.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1585791-20210414.htm&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvkYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=e44ce299\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1585791-20210414.htm&h=2651d191\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1585791-20210414.htm</a>"},{"pid":"4a6c933375c110652bb910e2644f0801a6a6f396","tid":2488781,"uid":255637,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T12:49:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />直接出人仔做糧啦 出乜鳩港紙姐"},{"pid":"453183fb0a6f0287d83b2509b6581947b61c0062","tid":2488781,"uid":68111,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T12:56:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幾時幫佢地捐糧 展示愛國情懷"},{"pid":"3ce66bcda8e9826af966ad2fa211aaa9743c7286","tid":2488781,"uid":103156,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T12:56:55.000Z","msg":"講情懷就要加埋「心口碎大石」、「滾油中取物」、「吞熱炭」、「金鐘罩縮陽，任踢下陰」、「鐵布衫擋刀槍」等表演"},{"pid":"