be/doURFQ9Lokk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdoURFQ9Lokk&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvkYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=fbc88205\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/doURFQ9Lokk</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T14:01:45.000Z","msg":"其實俄式正步不嬲踢得唔高<br />\n反而德式踢得高<br />\n下面有蘇聯同nazi嘅閱兵片<br />\n你會發覺普魯士式正步係高過 蘇聯<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/srhABN7UDFQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsrhABN7UDFQ&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvkYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=3efab8a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/srhABN7UDFQ</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YSvS4LY26Yg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYSvS4LY26Yg&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvkYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=d40dc1ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YSvS4LY26Yg</a><br />\n<br />\n至於北韓，其實我覺得係下身德式，上身蘇式<br />\n而亞洲人嘅身材問題我覺得係膊頭出事<br />\n通常太窄，同埋胸肌部分太薄<br />\n之前喺佐敦見過槍會山嘅老解放監<br />\n夠高，但感覺上係肌肉量不足"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T14:08:34.000Z","msg":"肌肉呢個真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俄仔個個館長咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過德式同蘇式其實最大分別就係壓唔壓腳尖 同埋蘇式正常係除咗領旗隊之外唔擺手 北韓係照搬蘇式 正宗野嚟 <br />\n同埋2020年嗰次夜晚閱兵開始終於轉返蘇式正步，結束左90年代開始嘅苦行軍 彈簧正步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n民國嗰隻你當佢係法式大擺臂+慢撥普魯士正步就會fit曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4e4f51c733c1f2188369267de4c073bc2f38717","tid":2488781,"uid":265521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T14:09:09.000Z","msg":"對宗主國俄羅斯的情懷"},{"pid":"f94cad31c6cf777b9ca37da7b67f592ed51441b0","tid":2488781,"uid":207949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96386088ed089fc4e9254fade1530b7d363ef20c","tid":2488781,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d4a47201afe50cf086c28725dbd344964625f172","tid":2488781,"uid":205469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score"